{"tid":903605,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"Vivian Maier 所見的色彩","createTime":"2018-11-15T16:23:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T12:17:12.000Z","uid":38218,"like":29,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"9b7769206f7b5374ef000343538c020275bf7428","tid":903605,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:23:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/rsscRprM/VM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FrsscRprM%2FVM.jpg&h=f4a1e874&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;A photograph is a secret about a secret.&rdquo; Diane Arbus曾道。Vivian Maier 嘅相片亦係個secret。由1950年代至其過身前幾年 (2009年去世，終年83歲)，共拍攝最少15萬張照片。主要攝於芝加哥，但從未展示於任何人。而最常見嘅拍攝題材就係佢嘅身影。多年以保姆為工作維持生計，但可能拎住相機遊走街角，拍攝一張又一張題材風趣、構圖豐富、自然流露嘅相片，先係佢真正嘅工作。佢曾經被一位相熟嘅男士質疑其職業，但當時無話自己係個保姆，反而答：「我係個間諜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」呢句亦正好描述所有絕佳嘅街拍攝影師。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Tw4mDp4c/car.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FTw4mDp4c%2Fcar.jpg&h=0773c66a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一切都要從2007年的一場機緣巧合嘅拍賣講起。事緣一位女士欠交儲物櫃的租金，結果櫃內嘅負片、沖曬相片、contact sheets同一卷卷未處理嘅菲林全部充公、並由一位Chicago嘅地產經紀 (John Maloof) 全數購入。當時除咗Vivian Maier 呢個名稱，其他有關其身份嘅事都係個謎。亦因為被John買咗，Maier隱密拍攝嘅作品先可以被大眾認識並傳頌。直至兩年後，John碰巧得悉Maier去世嘅消息，佢嘅故事先被發掘報導。 更將整個經歷拍成紀錄片 &ldquo;Finding Vivian Maier&rdquo; 並提名2015 年度嘅Oscars。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/hvXvWsML/vm-dpc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FhvXvWsML%2Fvm-dpc.jpg&h=e2958856&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n可能為咗鋪路成為認真嘅藝術家，Maier 皆拍攝彩色及黑白照片，而佢嘅黑白照係先被廣傳。Maier依家甚至與美國街攝嘅傳奇(例如Arbus, Robert Frank, Lee Friedlander, Lisette Model, Garry Winogrand)齊名。最近新書&rdquo;Vivian Maier: The Color Work&rdquo; 亦展示佢對鮮明影像嘅觸覺。<br />\nMaier嘅拍攝手法好原創，好似玩緊對比、比較嘅把戲。係閱覽Maier嘅照片集時總會令人聯想帶起其他攝影師。以下呢張就好似Thomas Struth ( 德國知名嘅museum photographer) 嘅攝影:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/tg9gCp2C/vm-TS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Ftg9gCp2C%2Fvm-TS.jpg&h=d34d35e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而呢張就聯想到Arbus 嘅玩具手榴彈男孩:<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/qBWyB6nJ/gun-VM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FqBWyB6nJ%2Fgun-VM.jpg&h=38f7c6d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nby Vivian Maier<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/x12mMrtB/grenade.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fx12mMrtB%2Fgrenade.jpg&h=1eb8cf95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nby Arbus<br />\n<br />\n呢架爛bumper嘅甲蟲車就想起Arnold Odermatt嘅一系列車禍照<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/k5jR02qd/bettle.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fk5jR02qd%2Fbettle.jpg&h=bc0d74f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nby Vivian Maier<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/434h26C5/crash.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F434h26C5%2Fcrash.jpg&h=5dd82238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nby Arnold Odermatt<br />\n車身上嘅黃色亦係佢好多佳作出現嘅顏色。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/dVs1JJWQ/balon.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FdVs1JJWQ%2Fbalon.jpg&h=f913c804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/h4NZFjtx/phone2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fh4NZFjtx%2Fphone2.jpg&h=532d80c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/y6TCsc29/flower.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2Fy6TCsc29%2Fflower.jpg&h=6e6016dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面呢張相攝於1975年。優雅嘅景觀區分Andy Warhol嘅絲網花朵圖案同 abstract expressionism (抽象表現主義) 嘅填滿構圖手法。同年，佢係行人道上下兩位男士。照片中三位行人嘅衣著皆充滿極嘅陽光氣色出奇地無一個係笑緊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/YCWXqwjV/pass.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FYCWXqwjV%2Fpass.jpg&h=d06bac65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nMaier 能夠將充滿故事性嘅細節用一張照片完整表達。<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/5NF58S1Q/peep.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F5NF58S1Q%2Fpeep.jpg&h=079a26da&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面照片中嘅伴侶泳池外窺看泳客的活動。婦人灰白嘅捲髮與牆身灰泥哽嘅顏相似，深橙色泳褲嘅紋理同池邊嘅軟墊相近。男士背上雀斑亦襯托牆上嘅質地。從耳旁望去泳池對面嘅深髮女士，其藍色泳衣比池水更深色，並高舉雙手，好似置身於狂歡嘅晚會。從外面觀看，甚至聞到池水嘅氯氣，情況比隔住塊璃貼頭凝視更慘。婦人手中緊握嘅啡色紙袋令整個場景變得傷感。<br />\n一直有個令人困擾嘅問題就係竟一個保姆點樣可以影到咁高質素嘅作品。或許承認呢樣就係性別歧視。皆因無人會疑點解Henry Darger (作家及術家) 一個醫院守衛可創造出一萬五千頁嘅文學巨著。攝影師Joel Meyerowitz 係新書序言內道，Maier 彩色攝影界嘅詩人。佢好似穿上偉大街拍攝影師嘅隱身袍。&ldquo;She&rsquo;s as plain as an old-fashioned schoolmarm. She&rsquo;s the wallflower, the spinster aunt, the ungainly tourist in the big city .&thinsp;.&thinsp;. except .&thinsp;.&thinsp;. she isn&rsquo;t!&rdquo; 唔知 Bresson (布列松) 嘅決定性時刻都可以其外表定義呢？<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/L5WT2yS2/ball.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FL5WT2yS2%2Fball.jpg&h=6a5a9747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/8kXwRC69/boy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F8kXwRC69%2Fboy.jpg&h=375053c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/cCCmppVF/feet.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FcCCmppVF%2Ffeet.jpg&h=0fe94ab8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/YS2bNLdc/vm2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FYS2bNLdc%2Fvm2.jpg&h=aee00dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSource: <a href=\"https://www.newyorker.com/culture/photo-booth/what-vivian-maier-saw-in-color\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newyorker.com%2Fculture%2Fphoto-booth%2Fwhat-vivian-maier-saw-in-color&d=w6KT%2BKEW50acgijZ%2FDEmhcKJ7zzy8RXHrd%2FDXtMH0Y8%3D&h=991e320b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newyorker.com/culture/photo-booth/what-vivian-maier-saw-in-color</a>"},{"pid":"32a2907e7ff6205f3adbf89c9789e8f6d1b6befb","tid":903605,"uid":6848,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"佢既自拍真係好impressive<br />\n每次睇都覺得佢係未來去左1950年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NFuZK8P.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNFuZK8P.png&h=3f044ede&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qP3r9Aw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqP3r9Aw.png&h=68aaf07d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WmjZK8S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWmjZK8S.png&h=53540cca&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EpmtDtU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEpmtDtU.png&h=8813dde8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外contact sheets都好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KOjK86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KOjK86.png&h=80807b3b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HVDWNns.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHVDWNns.png&h=a74102d3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep7Mp88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep7Mp88.png&h=d24c05ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7AigfQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7AigfQ.png&h=691f546a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8efe6447e44a5dcdaa6e7b11f501e326d64c2d9e","tid":903605,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-15T16:57:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ep7Mp88.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fep7Mp88.png&h=d24c05ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T7AigfQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7AigfQ.png&h=691f546a&s={SIZE}\" /